sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant DB as Dashboard
    participant Modules as Learning<br/>Modules
    participant Backend as Backend
    participant AI as Groq API
    participant Supabase as Supabase

    User->>DB: 1. Opens Dashboard
    DB->>Supabase: Fetch user data
    Supabase-->>DB: Return stats & readiness
    DB-->>User: Display analytics

    User->>Modules: 2. Select Learning Path
    Modules->>Backend: Request content
    Backend->>Supabase: Get module data
    Supabase-->>Modules: Return content
    Modules-->>User: Display module

    User->>Modules: 3. Take Mock Interview / Solve Challenge
    Modules->>AI: Send user input
    AI-->>Modules: Return evaluation & feedback
    Modules-->>User: Display result

    Modules->>Backend: 4. Update progress
    Backend->>Supabase: Save: streak +1, badges, XP
    Supabase-->>Modules: Confirmed
    Modules-->>User: Show rewards earned

    User->>DB: 5. View updated profile
    DB->>Supabase: Refresh stats
    Supabase-->>DB: Return updated data
    DB-->>👤User: Display new readiness & leaderboard

